Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.65,0:00:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm feeling strangely cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.16,0:00:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san, let's get closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.73,0:00:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.87,0:00:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.71,0:00:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your hand off him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.66,0:00:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How nonchalant of you to keep pushing yourself closer one night after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.94,0:00:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito is my familiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been ordered by Henrietta-sama to be his maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.90,0:00:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.05,0:00:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all in the same room, so there's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all sleep together peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.35,0:00:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:41.31,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See whom Saito-san chooses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's completely devoted to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.25,0:00:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's just a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.07,0:01:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like how birds think whatever they see first is their mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.54,0:01:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so confident, then you will not\Nmind having a match over him, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already know he'll choose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.73,0:01:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.65,0:01:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During the Sleipnir Ball tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if Saito-san manages to find Miss Vallière, I'll give up on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.28,0:01:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he can't find you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.69,0:01:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're not confident after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.46,0:01:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.77,0:01:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act high and mighty just because you have big breasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cow boob!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a loser's cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine what'll come next.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and what's Sleipnir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleipnir is a ball held at the beginning of the new semester.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's happening tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why a ball for the new semester?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a welcome, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an opportunity for me to teach the newly\Nadmitted ladies about adult social occasions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard about the monster bird that's been appearing near the border recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.63,0:04:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it's incredibly huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My brother who is a dragon knight was talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's no ordinary ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a costume ball party.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.71,0:04:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using the Mirror of Truth, you use magic to garment yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can take the form you most wish to become.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how many people will look like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm the world's most handsome guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to become, Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.33,0:04:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you give me the details of that rumour?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened some nights ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dragon knight on a patrol looked up into the sky and saw...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's said that it had to be at least 150 mail long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's the legendary giant dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, apparently its wing shape is completely different from that of a dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.14,0:05:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But by the time a squad of dragon knights had taken off after receiving the report, there was no sign of it anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got to be a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the only Void mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's up to something again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.36,0:05:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to tell Louise to watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Vallière has gone out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.19,0:05:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing on the floor?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... actually, recently read a book called "Maid Afternoon".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maid Afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. A story of a young maid working at an aristocrat's manor...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the lord forces indecent things on the maid at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:06:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking I wouldn't mind that\Nhappening to me if it's Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my gosh! I broke my master's cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your turn, Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My turn? What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my gosh! I broke my master's cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Punish me as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peek.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put an end to this, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We... We will...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.05,0:06:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maid! Familiar! Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:56.97,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:07:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sleipnir Ball's today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.13,0:07:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are to find me no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.89,0:07:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.58,0:07:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you pick up where we left off last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick up where we left off last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.88,0:07:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.23,0:07:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair, Miss Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't tempt him like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.26,0:07:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear students who have gathered here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to take you to tonight's mirage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the Mirror of Truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.08,0:07:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enter one at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine your ideal appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.68,0:08:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This mirror will look into the deep part of your heart and transform you into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, imagine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chii-neesama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be the giant monster bird everyone's been talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:09:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it appeared above the academy, is it after Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to tell Louise about this right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! Today's a costume ball party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is to make you understand that in this academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,family, status, nationality or rank do not matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.25,0:09:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, it would be impossible to study together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Additionally, we have Queen Henrietta as our guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, to promote the purpose of the ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she is in disguise as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to identify the queen is an interesting game to play, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure all of you work hard to become the ideal person you wish to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, the party has started.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, start changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I always wanted to be a dragon knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to be the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I would turn into a cute girl like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to getting disguised?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.86,0:10:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am disguised.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to an ideal form with both beauty and talent,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there isn't any other than myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There has to be a limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.01,0:10:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to how shameless one can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-She's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, who have taken the form of such a beautiful lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask for your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:10:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Osmond.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if we all disguise as Tiffania, we can't tell who's who!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you taking so much time, Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come find me already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with those breasts?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.85,0:11:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice. Is that you, Louise-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.24,0:11:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I got to become Saito-san, whom I aspire to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for some reason, my breasts didn't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tiffa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, I can't tell who's who!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right here, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.29,0:12:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.12,0:12:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, for a costume party,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no one's wearing a costume, let alone any masks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.87,0:12:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that was easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure it was all right to make that kind of promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You forgot already?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, um... Who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm me, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...really Saito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... Anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a giant monster bird outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm here, so it should be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, um, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.28,0:12:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the promise bothers you so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind picking up where we left off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Picking up? Picking up what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.30,0:13:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really afraid of a tiny spider like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.44,0:13:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come find me already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I will take the void mage as a gift for Joseph-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The magic wore off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The party's not over yet, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a problem! The Mirror of Truth is broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Today's a ball party where you disguise yourself using magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disguise using magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I completely thought you were Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was also magically disguised as the person I feel is my ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is only natural you did not recognise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ideal?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.98,0:14:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am jealous of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How pure her heart is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How she can stand up for her own justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had even a fraction of her courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would not have had to commit a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:15:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mistake?! You haven't done anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.45,0:15:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.54,0:15:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! You got it wrong! Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? I don't get it! I don't understand him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.08,0:15:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you, Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a big, stupid traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were with the Princess of all people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.35,0:15:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has this been going on for long?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:15:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been sneaking behind my back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:16:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that. That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it not? I saw it with my own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I mistook her as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.08,0:16:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also through a turn of events...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from me! I hate you, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Tabitha.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.48,0:16:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, which way did Louise go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're horrible. You're absolutely horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive you. I can't forgive you, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So have your revenge on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.59,0:16:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're a great Void mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.73,0:16:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheffield!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, coming all the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. The only people who can truly\Nunderstand you are other Void mages.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe a word of what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whom do you believe in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.37,0:17:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your familiar? Or the Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I am your ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.34,0:17:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't betray me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you attack me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.32,0:17:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Order? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's taking you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were the monster bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.14,0:18:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way, Tabitha.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.66,0:18:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or else I'll have to beat you to save Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course she won't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's Chevalier de Norfatul.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our loyal watchdog.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watchdog?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not looking too good. She looks pretty serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.20,0:18:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha, stop this! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imotal Iisan Hagaras.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Javelin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? You could have killed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.85,0:18:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I hurt someone who has saved us numerous times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.82,0:19:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's to protect Louise, I couldn't do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you taking your time for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.41,0:19:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tabitha?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have the Void in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.01,0:19:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless. She's deep asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.77,0:19:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump off there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand the situation you're in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you, Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:20:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you! I hate you! I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop jumping around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you what happened was just how things turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you! Let go of me! I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.48,0:20:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one for me, Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, what a trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you believe me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really, really mean this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.86,0:20:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The most important person in the world... Louise...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.95,0:21:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner. Sorry to bother you when you're busy,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we're surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.09,0:21:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take her away by force now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gandalfr.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.91,0:21:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.22,0:21:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The monster bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.42,0:21:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing I was passing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.21,0:21:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colbert-sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.01,0:21:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.38,0:22:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.00,0:23:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you always looking at the Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.58,0:23:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dog. You're hiding something from me, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.34,0:23:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero no Tsukaima. Princess no Rondo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.44,0:23:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eastern Pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.11,0:23:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.87,0:23:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you if you look away.
